---
import PeopleMeeting from "../assets/people-meeting.avif";
---

<div class="container flex items-center justify-between p-12 bg-white mx-auto">
  <div class="grow-0 px-5 w-1/2 hidden md:block">
    <picture class="w-full">
      <img
        src={PeopleMeeting.src}
        class="h-auto w-5/6 object-cover"
        alt="A group of people in a business meeting"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </picture>
  </div>
  <div class="md:w-1/2">
    <p class="text-4xl solway-medium text-cool-green">About Us</p>
    <p class="leading-8 py-4 manrope-light">
      We specialize in <span class="manrope-bold">Forum Peer Groups</span>,
      creating transformative spaces for professionals to connect, reflect, and
      grow. Alongside our peer group expertise, we offer General Facilitation
      Services that foster open dialogue and collaboration across teams.
    </p><p class="leading-8 py-4 manrope-light">
      With a growing community of over 40 members across 6 countries our
      expertly facilitated experiences are designed to meet people where they
      areâ€”both personally and professionally.
    </p>
    <div class="py-10 lg:hidden mx-auto w-full text-center">
      <a href="team" class="no-underline">
        <button
          class="rounded-full bg-orange-300 text-orange-800 font-bold p-2 flex-nowrap manrope-bold text-xl md:text-2xl px-8"
          >Meet the Team</button
        >
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
